<div class="container text-center text-light pt-3 bg-black">
    <div class="mb-4 mt-3 px-3">
        <img src="/images/holdItLogoColorFixed.svg" class="mb-3">
        <p class="lead pt-2 pb-2" style="font-size: .8rem;">Welcome to Hold It! What are we exactly? Well we're a breath hold tracker for the Wim Hof Method of course! What's the Wim Hof Method you say? First off, you ask a lot of questions. Second, hit the link down below to learn about Wim Hof and his methods, he's fascinating.</p><hr>
        <p class="lead pt-2 pb-2" style="font-size: .8rem;">When you're done, come back here and have fun tracking your holds and seeing other's progress. There's so much more we have in store for you, but for the time being please pardon our dust, we're just getting started...</p>
        
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <a href="/breathholds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary fw-bold bg-dark border-0">View Holds</a>
            </div>
